OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,FResidents of a housing complex in
OL,7,FPlymouth may not be able to return
OL,8,Fhome for up to eight weeks, after
OL,9,Fengineers warned parts of the building
OL,10,Fcould be at risk of collapse.
OL,12,FPeople were given two hours' notice to
OL,13,Fleave Evolution Cove on Friday 20
OL,14,FMarch, after engineers discovered
OL,15,Fstructural damage in the 64-unit
OL,16,Fapartment block.
OL,18,FProperty management company Centrick
OL,19,Fsaid temporary accommodation has been
OL,20,Fprovided to residents, and work is
OL,21,Funderway to stabilise the building.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
