FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,FResident Jon Dingle has lived in a two-
OL,7,Fbed flat in Evolution Cove for around
OL,8,Fa year with his autistic son, and is
OL,9,Famong those who were ordered to leave
OL,10,Fon Friday evening.
OL,12,FHe told ITV News that the alternative
OL,13,Faccommodation he has been given is
OL,14,Funsuitable, and it's having a big
OL,15,Fimpact on his family.
OL,17,F"We were both told we'd have to move
OL,18,Finto hotel accommodation," Mr Dingle
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,F"That was totally inappropriate for my
OL,7,Fson. He would not have been able to
OL,8,Fdeal with that, especially at such
OL,9,Fshort notice, so he had to go and stay
OL,10,Fwith his mother.
OL,12,F"We were told we'd get like-for-like
OL,13,Faccommodation. I've gone from my two-
OL,14,Fbed apartment with my son living with
OL,15,Fme, to a bedsit with no hot water and
OL,16,Fmy son living with his quite unwell
OL,17,Fmother."
OL,19,FHe added: "This is having such a
OL,20,Fdetrimental effect on my son, on his
OL,21,Fmum, and that whole family unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,F"My son lives with me. He's my
OL,7,Fresponsibility. I'm his carer. I don't
OL,8,Fthink any of that has really been
OL,9,Ftaken into consideration so far."
OL,11,FIn a letter sent to residents on
OL,12,FFriday, 20 March, Centrick said
OL,13,Finvestigations into cracks in
OL,14,Fstructural beams in Evolution Cove's
OL,15,Fcar park had revealed more work was
OL,16,Fneeded to support the building load.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,FThe company said: "Until the
OL,7,Fadditional props to support the
OL,8,Fbuilding are installed, we have been
OL,9,Fadvised that there is a risk of
OL,10,Fbuilding collapse."
OL,12,FResidents were told to pack essential
OL,13,Fbelongings, including medication and
OL,14,Fimportant documents, and to meet a
OL,15,FCentrick representative at
OL,16,Fapproximately 7pm to organise
OL,17,Falternative accommodation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,FCllr Chris Penberthy, cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor housing, cooperative development
OL,8,Fand communities, said: "I arrived just
OL,9,Fafter seven o'clock, there were people
OL,10,Fon the pavement, there was no one from
OL,11,Fthe company around."
OL,13,F"People were distressed, there were
OL,14,Fchildren who'd not had their tea,
OL,15,Fthere were people with
OL,16,Fvulnerabilities, there were other
OL,17,Fpeople in the building, and that was
OL,18,Fthe case for quite a long time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,F"It seemed to me that whatever is
OL,7,Fhappening to the building, the way
OL,8,Fresidents were treated on Friday
OL,9,Fevening wasn't the best."
OL,11,FProperty owner Grey GR estimates it
OL,12,Fcould take six to eight weeks until
OL,13,Fpeople can return to their homes.
OL,15,FA representative from Grey GR said:
OL,16,F"Grey's top priority is the safety and
OL,17,Fwellbeing of residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774285870
OL,3,CResidents face weeks away from home
OL,4,Camid risk of apartment block collapse
OL,6,F"Grey GR, Centrick and our alternative
OL,7,Faccommodation partners are working
OL,8,Ftirelessly and quickly to find the
OL,9,Fbest possible accommodation for
OL,10,Fresidents, taking into account any
OL,11,Fvulnerabilities or special
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,F"Where any residents have contacted us
OL,15,Fabout their comfort with alternative
OL,16,Faccommodation, we have responded
OL,17,Fquickly and have confirmed that we are
OL,18,Fsourcing alternatives."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
